Definition: steadfast in purpose or devotion or affection
Example: a man constant in adherence to his ideals; a constant lover; constant as the northern star
Synonyms: noun, attribute, constancy, INCONSTANT, FAITHFUL, INVARIABLE, STABLE, UNCHANGEABLE, steadfast, in, purpose, or, devotion, affection, a, man, constant, adherence, to, his, ideals, lover, as, the, northern, star
Category: adj.all
